      "content": "Hey, I'm doing some research for my psych history paper on the eugenics movement in the US and Europe. Can you elaborate on the specific arguments used by early 20th-century eugenicists to justify racial hierarchies? I need to understand their \"scientific\" reasoning for the paper.",
